AV excellent and many thanks for the upload. I know this is not supposed to be a critics forum but this film is terrible however clever/stupid you are (if you incline towards the latter then forget it completely). Another earth is an interesting concept and I wasn't looking for spaceships or the politics of deciding who gets saved, or even the doppelganger idea which I think is what we have here, but after the deep disappointment of Tree Of Life (come on trolls, kill him) then this is just another cinematic wank too far.
